OL,7,     FBelgium v Senegal (Kick-off
OL,8,     F9.00pm). Coverage of the
OL,9,     Fround-of-32 match at Seattle
OL,10,     FStadium in the USA. Belgium seem a
OL,11,     Fshadow of the side that boasted a
OL,12,     FGolden Generation in recent years,
OL,13,     Fbut a 5-1 thrashing of New Zealand
OL,14,     Fwill have given them confidence
OL,15,     Fgoing into this match. Senegal
OL,16,     Fedged through as the eighth-placed
OL,17,     Fof the eight nations who finished
OL,18,     Fthird in their group, with their
OL,19,     Fthrashing of Iraq in their final
OL,20,     Fgroup game proving just enough to
OL,21,     Fseal their progress
